729066f-a.title: Richmond: Knesel Street - Rossville Avenue
729066f-a.text:
Enesel Street (center, from left to right), adjoining the N.E.
corner of Rossville Avenue, showing the site to be an empty lot. The
view is northward across En,esel Street from an empty lot on the south
side. The house shown fronts on Morris Street.
April 30, 1929.
P. L. Speer
